=== Key Principles

    - *Pacing is paramount*: More important than any medication or supplement
    - *Early intervention*: Treating mild disease aggressively may prevent severe disease
    - *Accommodations are essential*: Reduce work/study load to sustainable level
    - *Avoid GET*: Do not be pressured into graded exercise programs
    - *Target root causes*: Immune dysregulation, hormonal imbalance, microbiome - not just symptoms
    - *Hope with realism*: Some improve significantly; not all recover; pacing prevents worsening for most

